1
00:00:01,300 --> 00:00:03,960
你的巴尼叔叔总是有点神秘
Your Uncle Barney was always always a bit of an enigma.

2
00:00:03,970 --> 00:00:05,740
住在纽约的那些年里
In all the years we lived in New York,

3
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:08,460
我们当中没有一个人踏进 过他家的门槛
none of us had ever set foot in his apartment.

4
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:11,640
直到那天 某人甚至出现他的床上
Until one day, one of us did.

5
00:00:14,470 --> 00:00:16,050
这是个有趣的故事
It's a pretty good story.

6
00:00:16,060 --> 00:00:18,940
信不信由你 这一切和酒精都没有关系
And believe it or not, alcohol did not play a role.

7
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:21,760
所有的一切都开始于两周前 给莉莉的乔迁派对上
It all started two weeks earlier at Lily's housewarming.

8
00:00:21,810 --> 00:00:22,210
两周前
Hey, welcome to my new home.

9
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:24,260
欢迎光临寒舍

10
00:00:24,270 --> 00:00:27,040
莉莉 这就是
Oh, wow, Lily, this is...

11
00:00:27,290 --> 00:00:29,300
你的新公寓就这样?
Oh, this is all of it.

12
00:00:29,310 --> 00:00:31,950
是的 我知道是小了点 不过这就是特点
Yeah, I know it's small, but it's got character.

13
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:32,720
谢谢
Thank you.

14
00:00:32,730 --> 00:00:36,230
我最近在跟邻居学立陶宛语
And I am learning Lithuanian from my neighbors.

15
00:00:36,240 --> 00:00:37,080
他们真是太有意思了
They're great.

16
00:00:37,090 --> 00:00:38,710
你也看见了 他们总是在大堂那
They're always out there in the hall, you know,

17
00:00:38,740 --> 00:00:41,420
做饭 打牌 还相互剪头
cooking and gambling and giving each other haircuts.

18
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:42,910
真有趣
It's nice.

19
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:45,210
你的厨房和厕所是一起的?
Hey, is that a toilet in your kitchen?

20
00:00:45,220 --> 00:00:47,390
或者说炉子在你浴室?
Or a stove in your bathroom?

21
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:49,960
这个不是一般的炉子
Oh, that's not just a stove.

22
00:00:49,970 --> 00:00:51,630
这是炉皇(stovenkerator＝ stove+oven+sink+refrigerator)
That's a stovenkerator:

23
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:55,590
它集火炉 水池 烤箱还有冰箱为一体
a combination of a stove, oven and sink and refrigerator.

24
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,930
炉皇
Stovenkerator.

25
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:58,430
是不是很酷啊 超现实主义
Isn't that futuristic?

26
00:00:58,440 --> 00:00:59,880
我的神啊 怎么这样
God, I hope not.

27
00:00:59,890 --> 00:01:02,620
墨菲床很酷啊 (墨菲床：一种不用时可折起放进壁橱的床)
Hey, cool Murphy bed.

28
00:01:02,630 --> 00:01:05,970
是啊 有点乱 今早懒得整理了 所以
Yeah, it's kind of a mess. I didn't make my bed this morning, so...

29
00:01:05,988 --> 00:01:07,323
Oh!

30
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:12,630
你知道吗? 有个新说法
You know what, I bet sleeping at this angle is good for you.

31
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,240
以这个角度入睡对身体有利
For some reason.

32
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:16,050
我明白了
I got it.

33
00:01:20,940 --> 00:01:25,100
他是说 什么 什么 我就要 什么 什么
That was, something, something, I am going to, something,

34
00:01:25,110 --> 00:01:28,230
你是一个 什么 什么 驴
you like a, something, donkey.

35
00:01:28,255 --> 00:01:29,720
Huh.

36
00:01:29,870 --> 00:01:31,890
多么奇特的文化啊
Other cultures.

37
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:34,730
不要管他了 我来看看你们送的果篮
Hey, let's break out the fruit basket.

38
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:36,860
奇怪?有谁吃把它吃了
Hey, who ate all the...?

